The use of automated generation procedures and algorithms suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the emphasis on formal correctness and verification suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
